      - lineIndex: 14
        speakerName: Ozric
      - lineIndex: 15
        speakerName: Ozric
      normalCardDialogueLines:
      - Ozric studies you for a moment.
      - "\u201CI\u2019m sorry... but I believe I\u2019ve said all I can.\u201D"
      - He folds his hands neatly.
      - "\u201CSometimes what you\u2019re looking for is not where you are searching.\u201D"
      - "\u201CIn time, you will find your path.\u201D"
      - "\u201CBut I believe, you won\u2019 find it through me.\u201D"
      - He bows his head slightly.
      - "\u201CMay the Flesh guide you.\u201D"
      - Without another word, Ozric quietly leaves.
