  - characterName: Bramble
    characterObject: {fileID: 942175340}
    characterButton: {fileID: 942175342}
    characterRectTransform: {fileID: 942175341}
    normalPosition: {x: 230, y: -249}
    focusedPosition: {x: -690, y: -107}
    introLinesBeforeChoices:
    - "\u201CWonderful!\u201D"
    - "\u201CI was beginning to think I\u2019d have to eat all of this myself.\u201D\r\n"
    - Bramble slides a Bowl of stew to you.
    - "\u201CEat!\u201D"
    - "\u201CTrust me. Breakfast is the best meal around here.\u201D"
    - "\u201CActually, lunch is pretty good too\u2026 and dinner!\u201D\r\n"
    - "\u2026"
    - "\u201CI just like food.\u201D"
    - He laughs
    - "\u2026"
    - "\u201CHow\u2019d you sleep?\u201D"
    - "\u201CHopefully better than me\u2026 I dreamt I was chased by chickens.\u201D"
    - "\u201CTerrifying creatures\u2026\u201D"
    - You laugh.
    - "\u201CChickens?\u201D"
    - He grins.
    - "\u201CI\u2019m glad you\u2019re laughing.\u201D"
    - "\u201CMost spend their first morning staring down at their plate.\u201D"
    - "\u201CI know I did.\u201D"
    - "\u2026"
    - ' Bramble tears of a piece of bread and hands it to you.'
    - "\u201CActually, when I first arrived, I cried for three days straight.\u201D"
    - He laughs awkwardly.
    - "\u201CNot my proudest moment\u2026\u201D"
    - "\u201CBut everyone was really kind.\u201D"
    - '"Well, almost everyone."'
    - ...
    - '"Ozric barely spoke a word."'
    - '"Ash kept to himself."'
    - '"But I figured eventually we''d all become friends."'
    - '"Life''s easier that way."

'
    - '...

'
    - '"Say..."'
    - '"You don''t regret coming here, do you?"'
    - ' Bramble pauses.

'
    - '"Because I''d hate to think I made a new friend only for them to disappear."'
    - "\u2026"
    - ' Something about his words catches your attention.'
    - Suddenly, you remember cards in your pocket.
