      specialCard: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b39c6c6934c77a54689c1f3befc1752c, type: 2}
      specialRouteFlag: BRAMBLEESCAPE
      normalRouteFlag: GAMEOVER
      specialCardDialogueLines:
      - Bramble chuckles at you being visibly off guard by his question.
      - "\u201CI can see what you really think.\u201D"
      - Bramble leans forward and looks into your eyes.
      - "\u201CDid you know everyone runs to the square when the evening bell rings?\u201D"
      - "\u201CEvery. Single. Time.\u201D"
      - "\u201CLike they are trained. Or scared something might happen if they don\u2019t...\u201D"
      - ...
      - He grins.
      - "\u201CWouldn\u2019t take much to get everybody\u2019s attention.\u201D"
      - Bramble comes even closer. Whispering.
      - "\u201CI know you don\u2019t like it here.\u201D"
      - "\u201CI can see it in your eyes. They never lie...\u201D"
      - "\u201CAnd I need you to promise me not to tell anyone.\u201D"
      - "\u201CBut there is a world out there. Purpose. Freedom.\u201D"
      - "\u201CBut I can\u2019t see that world without your help.\u201D"
      - "\u201CWe\u2019ll talk later.\u201D"
      - "\u201CToo many eyes and ears.\u201D"
      - ...
