      - lineIndex: 16
        speakerName: Bramble
      normalCardDialogueLines:
      - Bramble smiles sadly.
      - "\u201CHeh... I can tell, you know.\u201D"
      - "\u201CYou\u2019ve got that look.\u201D"
      - "\u201CLike someone who\u2019s already made up their mind.\u201D"
      - ...
      - "\u201CAnd that\u2019s alright. I won\u2019t stand in your way.\u201D"
      - "\u201CI\u2019d rather be a good memory than another regret.\u201D"
      - He forces a smile.
      - "\u201CBesides... I think you\u2019ve already established your next move.\u201D"
      - "\u201COr... the universe just doesn\u2019t have a plan for us together.\u201D"
      - ...
      - "\u201CJust promise me one thing.\u201D"
      - "\u201CDon\u2019t disappear without saying farewell.\u201D"
      - ...
