  nextSceneButton: {fileID: 0}
  autoNextSceneName: SeventhAct
  introDialogueLines:
  - "As you leave the hall alongside the other members, you\u2019re met with sweet
    and herby\r\nnotes."
  - Long wooden tables filled with different foods have been set up.
  - The others start feasting, laughing and chatting.
  - Some wave as you pass, others greet you with warm smiles.
  - 'For a moment, you forget where you are.

'
  - "Everything feels\u2026 normal."
  - "\u2026"
  - Brother Garrick approaches you from behind.
  - He places a hand on your shoulder.
  - "\u201CDo not be shy.\u201D\r\n"
  - "\u201CNo soul should break their fast alone.\u201D"
  - With that, he disappears into the crowd.
  - "\u2026"
  - Your gaze wanders across the gathering.
  - Bramble notices you immediately.
  - "\u201CThere you are!\u201D"
  - He enthusiastically waves a loaf of bread in the air.
  - "\u201CCome! Sit with me!\u201D\r\n"
  - "\u2026"
  - "Not far \u2013 Ozric sits alone."
  - His posture is straight.
  - A bowl of untouched stew before him.
  - His eyes are closed. He is praying.
  - "\u2026"
  - He opens his eyes and notices you looking at him.
  - He gives you a nod, gesturing you to join him.
  - "\u2026"
  - Who should you join?
  afterNoteDialogueLines: []
  choices: []
  endingLines:
  - Eventually, the morning feast comes to an end.
  - One by one, the members return to their duties
  - You decide to spend the rest of the day resting.
  - Evening is still far.
  - Perhaps a few hours of peace will do you some good.
  - You return to your cabin.
  - ...
  - And before long, you drift into a light sleep.
  useCardChoiceAfterEnding: 0
  maxDisplayedCardChoices: 9
  endingCardChoiceSettings:
    specialCard: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 176908487252b3f47a5936f2e98a5858, type: 2}
    specialRouteFlag: Ash Burn the Cult
    normalRouteFlag: Ash Ending false
    specialCardDialogueLines:
    - "Ash let\u2019s out a quiet chuckle."
    - "\u201COf course he didn\u2019t\u201D"
    - He tosses another piece of wood into the fire.
    - "\u201CLet me put it this way...\u201D"
    - "\u201CPeople come here looking for salvation.\u201D"
    - "\u201CA second chance.\u201D"
    - "\u201CA place to belong.\u201D"
    - ...
    - "\u201CAnd most of them find exactly that. At least for a while.\u201D"
    - "\u201CThe Leader has a talent for telling people what they need to hear.\u201D"
    - "\u201CThey stop asking questions.\u201D"
    - "\u201CPerhaps that\u2019s why Garrick never talks about the truth behind this
      place.\u201D"
    - "\u201CIf he did, some people might want to leave before they\u2019ve become
      comfortable.\u201D"
    - ...
    - "\u201CWell has anyone ever actually left this place then?\u201D"
    - Ash freezes.
    - ...
    - "\u201CWhy would you ask that?\u201D"
    - "You aren\u2019t sure."
    - The thought simply appeared.
    - 'Ash studies you for a moment before taking a quick look towards the sleeping

      cabins.'
    - "\u201CNot openly... well not that I\u2019ve seen...\u201D"
    - The fire crackles.
    - "\u201CYet somehow we never seem to run out of empty rooms.\u201D"
    - "\u201CStrange, isn\u2019t it.\u201D"
    - You stand up.
    - Quietly you make your way back to your cabin.
