    - lineIndex: 24
      speakerName: Ash
    normalCardDialogueLines:
    - "\u201CWhatever you were trying to do... it won\u2019t work.\u201D"
    - "\u201CI thought I could trust you, but seems you are just like the others.\u201D"
    - "\u201CI think it\u2019s time for you to leave me alone now.\u201D"
    - ...
    - "\u201CI said leave.\u201D"
    - You stand up.
    - Quietly you make your way back to your cabin.
